column5: A couple of nice of smallies from the St. Lawrence river.
nice bass and a well worn fish'n hat!
Great job on those beauties Larry Thanks for sharing Leechman
St. Lawrence especially Lake St. Francis is sick! Nice fish.  I plan on getting some like that in the next few weeks.
whoa.. nice footballs there  the feed bag is on!
Some nice fall Pumpkins right there....
Very nice! I'm assuming you caught them on tubes?Thanks for sharing.
Incredibly nice fish there, Larry. Thanks for sharing.
Larry, those are some real toads theres. Nickles? Im thinking yer under.  Very nice fish there.

Awsome job Larry, if you aren't catching monster Muskies then it's huge Bass. Job well done. Have you figured out yet if you fish out of a musky boat or a bass boat? You can't have both or is one in disguise...lol  Dirk
